ry automatically depending on the page in which this block is displayed. In the specific case of a hierarchical post type with taxonomies, the breadcrumbs can either reflect its post hierarchy (default) or the hierarchy of its assigned taxonomy terms.":["P\u0159esn\u00fd typ zobrazen\u00fdch drobe\u010dk\u016f se automaticky m\u011bn\u00ed v z\u00e1vislosti na str\u00e1nce, na kter\u00e9 je tento blok zobrazen. V konkr\u00e9tn\u00edm p\u0159\u00edpad\u011b hierarchick\u00e9ho typu p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvku s taxonomiemi mohou drobe\u010dky odr\u00e1\u017eet bu\u010f hierarchii p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f (v\u00fdchoz\u00ed nastaven\u00ed), nebo hierarchii p\u0159i\u0159azen\u00fdch taxonomick\u00fdch term\u00edn\u016f."],"Prefer taxonomy terms":["Up\u0159ednost\u0148ovat taxonomick\u00e9 term\u00edny"],"Term template block display setting\u0004Grid view":["Zobrazen\u00ed m\u0159\u00ed\u017eky"],"Term template block display setting\u0004List view":["Zobrazen\u00ed seznamu"],"Display the terms' names and number of posts assigned to each term.":["Zobrazit n\u00e1zvy term\u00edn\u016f a po\u010det p\u0159\u00edsp\u011bvk\u016f p\u0159i\u0159azen\u00fdch ke ka\u017ed\u00e9mu term\u00ednu."],"Name & Count":["Jm\u00e9no a po\u010det"],"Display the terms' names.":["Zobrazit n\u00e1zvy term\u00edn\u016f."],"When specific terms are selected, only those are displayed.":["Pokud jsou vybr\u00e1ny konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed term\u00edny, zobraz\u00ed se pouze ty."],"When specific terms are selected, the order is based on their selection order.":["Pokud jsou vybr\u00e1ny konkr\u00e9tn\u00ed term\u00edny, po\u0159ad\u00ed se \u0159\u00edd\u00ed po\u0159ad\u00edm jejich v\u00fdb\u011bru."],"Selected terms":["Vybran\u00e9 term\u00edny"],"Show nested terms":["Zobrazit vno\u0159en\u00e9 term\u00edny"],"Display terms based on specific criteria.":["Zobrazit term\u00edny na z\u00e1klad\u011b konkr\u00e9tn\u00edch krit\u00e9ri\u00ed."],"Display terms based on the current taxonomy archive. For hi